config MTK_HW_SEMAPHORE
	tristate "MediaTek mm hw semaphore driver"
	depends on ARCH_MEDIATEK || COMPILE_TEST
	help
	  This driver is for the Multimedia Infrastructure in MediaTek SoCs.
	  The hw semaphore driver mainly help power control, For checking the
	  real power status, such as mminfra, display, camera, mdp and video
	  codec.
